MonDX is a basic DX cluster client.

The objective of MonDX is to provide a free software that runs in Linux, OSX and Windows.
MonDX will provide hamradio DX-Cluster client.

Check http://www.mondx.org and http://jaime.robles.es for news & updates.


Read the INSTALL for installation purposes.
Read the changelog (windows users, rename to changelog.txt) to see the changes from one version to another.

Please send all your suggestions & bug reports.

I hope you enjoy MonDX!

73 de Jaime, EA4TV
